Description: Local Retrieval-Augmented Generation System
 A privacy-focused local RAG system that performs inference entirely on local
 hardware without internet dependency. Features embedded LLM and vector store
 with FastAPI web interface and rich CLI commands.
 .
 Key features:
  - 100% local processing with no cloud dependencies
  - Optimized for Raspberry Pi 5 and AMD64 systems
  - Dual hash strategy for intelligent content management
  - APT package installation with systemd service integration
  - Real-time streaming responses and progress tracking